Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在悄无声息中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何一个人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经改变 被红世的火炎包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了还在这里散步么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也省了我特地找你出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦只有一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊救命也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的讨伐者也同意破坏你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她...夏娜她...要把我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『远去的思念』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微能控制一点存在之力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经同意破坏密斯特斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是反对破坏密斯特斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果将“零时迷子”随即转移开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以防止于“假面舞会”正面冲突了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大规模的战斗会使世界的平衡崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到这点的话 我现在走的才是最有效的途径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在不清楚敌人下一步做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经被抓住主动权的时候这是最好的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还是异能者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样你也要反对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 海卡媞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星黎殿”在颤动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁佩奥尔那老太婆一直都在差使那疯子教授呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂之圣庙好像即将正式启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂之圣庙...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上也会忙起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要总在这里祈祷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷不如求我 海卡媞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所寻求的东西的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在寻求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须寻求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问多少次都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好她什么都没追寻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她能寻求到万物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能启动魂之圣庙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的对海卡媞无害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑心真重啊 千变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海卡媞会成为永恒的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和前所未有的存在之力一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽我所能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了保护我的海卡媞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海卡媞 你是纯真无暇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就永远这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一个红世之王都没能创造出的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“存在之泉”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能作出回答的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请别来妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜应该没能力反对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏娜是异能者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 “万条的使者”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有事要找这个密斯特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是要问他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的时候他好像关于红世之徒想说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是那红世之徒用过的那些鸟装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 他问过你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这点事情来阻止我破坏他么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说是芝麻小事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个密斯特斯偶尔总能体现出很强的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 之前的战斗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得先听一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...密斯特斯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密斯特斯的话...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么表情...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然如此执意...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你们说还需要他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这密斯特斯还有利用价值是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏暂时延期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只有这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁海尔密娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想对你失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才说的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些遗留下来的鸟装饰没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的红世之徒所使用的磷子的鸟装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些真的是用剩下的么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为还有什么危险性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不清楚红世之徒想做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们还没完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 不是没有这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好还是戒备一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还有利用价值吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是密斯特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而夏娜是异能者是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 我终于下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再让这个城市的人卷入战斗中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能保护大家的手段至此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护好这个城市和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市和大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想因为这种理由一起离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算离开城市 “假面舞会”的人也会追来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的红世之徒可能也会袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再去别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不行我们可以战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不行所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意思叫我留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要破坏我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为异能者这也是正确的办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的 我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你到底要我怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 夏娜在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从卡姆辛那里得到了这个护身符所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你感觉到封了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的...真的要离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能下定决心也有吉田的因素在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了我是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想以坂井悠二的身份来保护最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样想 也是自己是坂井悠二的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吉田对我的告白我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中 佐滕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井 我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是个坚强的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这个 我们能看到封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为大姐头回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没这么想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是红世之徒的话就准不开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛吉莉小姐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 玛吉莉小姐她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独这次不得不赞成坂井悠二了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没阻止你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个时候就已经向“万条的使者”挥剑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她却是如此的信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要坂井悠二怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说你希望他做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对悠二 对悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白 完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你杀了 然后把零子什么的藏到哪里去么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只要那样就很难再找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫“假面舞会”的红世之徒的集团\N也没理由再来袭击御崎市了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你会死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井...应该叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也这么说么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道夏娜怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异能者们总是不会把我们的事放心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非要离开这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经对这城市和家没什么迷恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是离开比较明智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让坂井一个人承受痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偶尔能回来次么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这么不坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有想见的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开城市这么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然如此轻易的说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里也那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原觉得和坂井同学的关系稍微拉近了点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在却觉得比之前还要遥远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去管她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那时开始 就不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在想是否要破坏我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在异能者眼里我只是个密斯特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那些装饰老老实实被烧掉的话就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那女佣是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个密斯特斯的洞察力很强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是使用过的东西也不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就看它直到被完全消灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都没感觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说点燃就是启动自在式的开关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁海尔密娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那有什么东西要出现在那自在式上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时是架飞空艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封绝!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星黎殿”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“假面舞会”的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“逆理之裁者”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁佩奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违啊 天壤之却火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有“万条的使者”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也没能察觉到这双重陷阱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异能者真是好战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“假面舞会”的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁佩奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大规模的举动会给世界带来多大的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点你就如此慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世中威名远扬的天壤之却火也堕落了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的大规模行动就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里即将成为存在之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之泉?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那种会冲出来废话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道他们想要的是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁海尔密娜 不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么灵敏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等密死特斯 我还要你帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被他们得手前破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护密斯特斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道该怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.70,0:24:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在“星黎殿”的悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”带来了前所未有的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寄托于希望的夏娜的决断的时刻也临近了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回『动摇的火焰』
